callToAction: NSLOCTEXT("", "317E560F4940D8BA7F253CA470A60407", "Recover the bones of the betrayers, the Horns of the Bull.")
description: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "80E593524AC3E263464404B388017A16", "The Lonely Shrine is an ash pyre of a legendary hero called the Vultauro the Bull. With his marauding horde, the Horns of the Bull, his battle prowess was revered by allies and feared by foes. If not for the ultimate betrayal and desertion of his troops, he would have commanded an unstoppable legion. Now, the only thing that will appease his spirits\' unrest is the return and burning of the bones of the marauders and the his once loyal warlords that led them.")
name: MIQ_0017_HOB_HornsOfTheBull
